context.arch.enactor
Class ClassifierEnactor

java.lang.Object
  context.arch.enactor.Enactor
      context.arch.enactor.ClassifierEnactor
Direct Known Subclasses:
AccelerometerEnactor, AutostatusEnactor
public class ClassifierEnactor
extends Enactor

Enactor that uses a WEKA classifier to model reasoning. Only one EnactorReference allowed that is automatically set up in the constructor.
